  "text": "Early studies showed that the biological activity of IAA-aa conjugates was related to the amount of free IAA detected in the stem tissue resulting from their hydrolysis [CITATION_1] . This demonstrated, for the first time, a direct link between the activity of the conjugates and their hydrolysis.",
